msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži najboljše rezultate…</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the high score table."
msgstr "Prikaže tabelo z najboljšimi rezultati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kolorlines;"
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kolorlines;"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will undo the last move."
msgstr "To bo razveljavilo zadnjo potezo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>End Turn</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Končaj potezo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skip your move, immediately play the next marbles without you moving any."
msgstr ""
"Preskočite svojo potezo, takoj odigrajte naslednje frnikole, ne da bi jih "
"premaknili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Left;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Left</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Left;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigacija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni levo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor to the left."
msgstr "To dejanje bo izbirni kazalec premaknilo v levo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Right;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Right</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Right;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigacija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni desno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor to the right."
msgstr "To dejanje bo izbirni kazalec premaknilo v desno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Up;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Up;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigacija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni gor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor up."
msgstr "To dejanje bo izbirni kazalec premaknilo navzgor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Down;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Down</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Down;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigacija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni navzdol</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor down."
msgstr "To dejanje bo izbirni kazalec premaknilo navzdol."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Select</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigacija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izberi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will select the item currently under the cursor."
msgstr "To dejanje bo izbralo element, ki je trenutno pod kazalcem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži naslednje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the information on next marbles."
msgstr "Preklopi informacije o naslednjih frnikolah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kolorlines; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kolorlines; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij "
"preberite razdelke o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-"
"settings\">meniju z nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &kolorlines; visual theme you can use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kolorlines;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Da Če želite spremeniti &kolorlines; vizualno temo lahko uporabite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kolorlines;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "I don't want to make any moves right now. Can I skip a turn?"
msgstr "Trenutno nočem narediti nobenih potez. Ali lahko preskočim potezo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To skip a turn you can use a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">keyboard shortcut</link>, or a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">menubar</link> option."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če želite preskočiti potezo, lahko uporabite <link linkend=\"menu-move-"
"endturn\">bližnjico na tipkovnici</link> ali možnost <link linkend=\"menu-"
"move-endturn\">menijske vrstice</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. You can use the cursor keys and the &Space; key to select and set the "
"marbles."
msgstr ""
"Da. Uporabite lahko smerne tipke in &Space; za izbiro in nastavitev frnikol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kolorlines; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. &kolorlines; nima funkcije <quote>Namig</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kolorlines; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kolorlines; trenutno nima funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolorlines; configuration dialog allows you to select &kolorlines; visual "
"themes."
msgstr ""
"&kolorlines; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da izberete "
"&kolorlines; vizualne teme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati novo temo, preprosto izberite temo na izbirnem seznamu. "
"Vsak element na seznamu prikazuje majhen predogled levo od imena teme. Izbor "
"se takoj uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton>, located at the bottom part of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste zadovoljni z izbrano temo, lahko kliknete <guibutton>Zapri</"
"guibutton>, ki se nahaja na dnu tega pogovornega okna."

